he error argument to MPI_INIT to&nbsp;INTEGER(KIND=4).</div><div><br></div><div>Kind regards,</div><div><br></div><div>Hristo</div><div><br><div><div>On 27.06.2012, at 20:34, Mohamad Ali Rostami wrote:</div><br class="Apple-interchange-newline"><blockquote type="cite">

